<title>NVIDIA BioNeMo Agent Toolkit 将生物分子模型转化为AI智能体在药物发现中的可调用技能</title>
<link>https://www.marktechpost.com/2026/06/29/nvidia-bionemo-agent-toolkit-turns-biomolecular-models-into-callable-skills-for-ai-agents-in-drug-discovery/</link>
<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.marktechpost.com/?p=80762</guid>
<pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 19:06:47 +0000</pubDate>
<source>marktechpost.com</source>
<description><![CDATA[【marktechpost.com】NVIDIA的开源BioNeMo Agent Toolkit将OpenFold3、DiffDock和GenMol等生物分子模型转化为有文档记录、可调用的AI智能体技能。每项技能描述了模型的目的、输入、产物和故障模式，使智能体能够选择、运行并解释它。在NVIDIA使用Codex CLI和GPT-5.5 fast进行的基准测试中，这些技能将任务完成率从57.1%提升至100%，并将代币效率提高了一倍。该文章NVIDIA BioNeMo Agent Toolkit Turns Biomolecular Models Into Callable Skills for AI Agents in Drug Discovery首次出现在MarkTechPost上。<br/><br/><a href="https://www.marktechpost.com/2026/06/29/nvidia-bionemo-agent-toolkit-turns-biomolecular-models-into-callable-skills-for-ai-agents-in-drug-discovery/">阅读原文</a>]]></description>
